**21.** If the annual interest rate is $7\%$, what will be the total amount (principal + interest) on Tk. $650$ after $6$ years?<br>
[DPDC Switch Board Attendant- 2021]

- a. Tk. 723
- b. Tk. 823
- c. `Tk. 923`
- d. Tk. 1023

+++ Solution:
$I = (650 \times 7 \times 6) / 100 = 273$

$\text{Total Amount} = 650 + 273 = 923$
+++

