**which.** If the annual interest rate is $6\%$, what will be the interest on Tk. $10,000$ for $9$ months?<br>
[25th BCS] + [Primary School (Asst. Teacher)-2024 (3rd Phase)] + [Ministry of Defence (Asst. Dir.)-2023] + [Palli Bidyut Samity (Meter Reader)-2024] + [DGDA (Office Asst.)-2024]

